divs: Sighting DetailsRadomly taking pictures of valley early in the morning. The dogs were barking and I thought a deer might be out there. I had my camera on burst and was holding the shutter button down. I took two pictures one after the other. The first one had this black thing in it. The second it's gone. I don't know what it is. I only saw it that night when I downloaded it on the computer. As I was looking at all the photos I had taken that day I found something else on the mountain top. The second picture shows the black something on the mountain. The last one is it moving away and a better shape to it. They move so fast that it would be hard to see them with the naked eye.
Summary: Black oval with two tails with white on the beginning or a light
